Parliament, Monday, 13 August 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Higher Education and Training will tomorrow meet with the Gender Commission in Parliament. The Gender Commission is expected to make a presentation on gender-based violence and gender transformation at tertiary institutions. Details of the meeting are as follows:Venue: V227
	Time: 09h00 ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON HIGHER EDUCATION AND TRAINING, MS CONNIE SEPTEMBER. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
